title._content: Roberta Frazier Anderson receiving award from Secretary of Agriculture Earl Butz

description._content: Original Collection: Extension and Experiment Station Communications (P 120) Item Number: P120:Acc 97:092 Image Description: Roberta Frazier Anderson was a Family Life Specialist for Oregon State University. For 15 years, Anderson instructed Extension and 4-H teachers on pertinent matters regarding family life, child development, and interpersonal communication.
